items.title: Almond | Skin Concealer
items.description:
Almond is a rich hazelnut ​with yellow undertones ​for deep skin tones.

DETAILS:

The Kylie Cosmetics Skin Concealer is a lightweight formula that provides medium buildable coverage for a skin-like finish. The long-wearing concealer, available in an all-inclusive range of 30 shades, gives a luminous finish that looks just like your skin, and is ideal for all skin types. The buildable formula allows you to achieve your desired level of coverage. Wear alone for a natural, dewy look or pair with your favorite setting powder for a matte finish. Perfect for spot concealing, lightening dark circles under the eyes and hiding imperfections. The paddle flock applicator makes application easy.

Formula Attributes:

• Creamy, lightweight formula blends seamlessly for instantly perfected skin
• Buildable coverage with a luminous satin skin-like finish
• Perfect for spot concealing, hiding imperfections, and brightening dark circles under the eyes
• Long wearing formula is water and sweat resistant

Key Ingredients:

• Infused with Alpha Hydroxy Acids (AHAs) that gently smooth the appearance of the skin's surface
• Keeps skin looking hydrated for easy application and extended wear
• Ultra fine powders blur the appearance of pores and wrinkles, and camouflage uneven skin tone

Contains:

  • 1 Skin Concealer (0.22 oz./ 6.3g)

items.title: Broad Spectrum SPF 30 Sunscreen Oil
items.description:
Available on KylieSkin.com GET FREE DOMESTIC SHIPPING for all orders over $30

SHIPS TO U.S. ADDRESSES ONLY

Kylie Skin Broad Spectrum SPF 30 Sunscreen Oil is an every day essential that helps protect skin from harmful UVA and UVB rays. This hydrating formula is filled with antioxidants and essential fatty acids like coconut oil and sunflower seed oil that help promote healthy looking skin and prolong moisture. Our non-messy, non-aerosol sprayer, makes for easy application, with our invisible formula gliding onto skin leaving zero white residue. No more streaky sunscreen, just glowing, hydrated, protected skin.

Size 3.9 fl oz / 115 ml

USAGE


Apply 30 minutes before sun exposure. Reapply every 90 minutes to two hours to help prevent sunburn and reduce the risk of skin cancer. Perfect for the beach, pool or anytime spent outdoors. Also great post-shower for a hydrating natural glow.

NOTE: Use caution, as oils can make a shower floor slippery. 

KEY FEATURES

  • Coconut Oil: A highly nourishing extract beloved for infusing skin with essential hydration that absorbs quickly for immediately visible results

  • Shea Butter: An exceptional moisturizer concentrated with natural fatty acids and vitamins known to smooth and soften skin

  • Grape Seed Oil: This weightless power-oil is non-comedogenic so it helps all skin types look youthful and healthy

  • Sunflower Seed Oil: An emollient super rich in Vitamin E to help skin retain vital moisture, and Omega-6 to help minimize inflammation and redness

|||

SIZE

3.9 fl oz / 115 ml

ACTIVE INGREDIENTS

Avobenzone 3% Sunscreen, Homosalate 10% Sunscreen, Octisalate 5% Sunscreen, Octocrylene, 10% Sunscreen

INACTIVE INGREDIENTS

Caprylic/Capric Triglyceride, Alcohol Denat., C12-15 Alkyl Benzoate, Octyldodecanol, Butyloctyl Salicylate, Polyamide-3 , Polyester-8, Diisopropyl Sebacate, Isodecyl Neopentanoate, Lauryl Lactate, Cocos Nucifera (Coconut) Oil, Elaeis, Guineensis (Palm) Oil, Actinidia Chinensis (Kiwi) Seed Oil, Butyrospermum Parkii (Shea) Butter, Helianthus Annuus (Sunflower) Seed Oil, Limnanthes Alba (Meadowfoam) Seed Oil, Raphanus Sativus (Radish) Seed Oil, Vitis Vinifera (Grape) Seed Oil, Fragrance, Diethylhexyl Syringylidenemalonate, Coumarin, Tocotrienols, Pentaerythrityl Tetra-Di-T-Butyl, Hydroxyhydrocinnamate, Tocopherol, Linalool, Alaria Esculenta Extract, Citric Acid

The Kylie Cosmetics Liquid Lipstick Lip Kit is your secret weapon to create the perfect 'Kylie Lip.' Each Lip Kit comes with a Matte Liquid Lipstick and Lip Liner.
    Lip Liner
    This ultra-long wearing Lip Liner has a creamy texture that glides across the lips for a very easy and comfortable application. The Lip Liner sharpens easily in most standard sized sharpeners - just make sure your sharpener is not dull!

items.title: KYLIE | Pencil Sharpener
items.description: The Kylie Cosmetics dual blade pencil sharpener is designed for multiple pencil sizes, and ideal for sharpening your favorite Kylie Cosmetics Lip Liners (from your Matte and Velvet Liquid Lipstick Lip Kits) to provide a precise application. Featuring a convenient cover to trap excess shavings, our new pencil sharpener can be used with lip pencils and eye liner pencils, to give you that perfect point. The new essential for your makeup bag!

Kylie's Notes

You guys know that Kylie Matte Lip Kit is one of my all time favorite Lip Kit shades. So I had to release my go-to shade as a velvet! I originally launched this in my 2019 Birthday collection, but it's back!

Each Lip Kit contains: 

  • 1 Velvet Liquid Lipstick (0.11 oz./ 3.0 g)

This ultra-long wearing Lip Liner has a creamy texture that glides across the lips for a very easy and comfortable application. The Lip Liner sharpens easily in most standard sized sharpeners - just make sure your sharpener is not dull!

I am obsessed with my Birthday Body Glow. After using my Coconut Body Lotion, I apply this to arms, legs, shoulders and anywhere I want to add a little soft shimmer. items.title: Sand | Skin Concealer
items.description:
Sand is a peachy light​​ ​with peach undertones ​for light skin tones.

DETAILS:

The Kylie Cosmetics Skin Concealer is a lightweight formula that provides medium buildable coverage for a skin-like finish. The long-wearing concealer, available in an all-inclusive range of 30 shades, gives a luminous finish that looks just like your skin, and is ideal for all skin types. The buildable formula allows you to achieve your desired level of coverage. Wear alone for a natural, dewy look or pair with your favorite setting powder for a matte finish. Perfect for spot concealing, lightening dark circles under the eyes and hiding imperfections. The paddle flock applicator makes application easy.

Formula Attributes:

• Creamy, lightweight formula blends seamlessly for instantly perfected skin
• Buildable coverage with a luminous satin skin-like finish
• Perfect for spot concealing, hiding imperfections, and brightening dark circles under the eyes
• Long wearing formula is water and sweat resistant

Key Ingredients:

• Infused with Alpha Hydroxy Acids (AHAs) that gently smooth the appearance of the skin's surface
• Keeps skin looking hydrated for easy application and extended wear
• Ultra fine powders blur the appearance of pores and wrinkles, and camouflage uneven skin tone

items.title: Toffee | Skin Concealer
items.description:
Toffee is a warm chestnut ​with yellow undertones ​for deep skin tones.

DETAILS:

The Kylie Cosmetics Skin Concealer is a lightweight formula that provides medium buildable coverage for a skin-like finish. The long-wearing concealer, available in an all-inclusive range of 30 shades, gives a luminous finish that looks just like your skin, and is ideal for all skin types. The buildable formula allows you to achieve your desired level of coverage. Wear alone for a natural, dewy look or pair with your favorite setting powder for a matte finish. Perfect for spot concealing, lightening dark circles under the eyes and hiding imperfections. The paddle flock applicator makes application easy.

Formula Attributes:

• Creamy, lightweight formula blends seamlessly for instantly perfected skin
• Buildable coverage with a luminous satin skin-like finish
• Perfect for spot concealing, hiding imperfections, and brightening dark circles under the eyes
• Long wearing formula is water and sweat resistant

Key Ingredients:

• Infused with Alpha Hydroxy Acids (AHAs) that gently smooth the appearance of the skin's surface
• Keeps skin looking hydrated for easy application and extended wear
• Ultra fine powders blur the appearance of pores and wrinkles, and camouflage uneven skin tone

Contains:

  • 1 Skin Concealer (0.22 oz./ 6.3g)
